#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/designing-packages.md
msgid "Package configuration is the default layer. The application can override it in its root package configuration.  Design for that:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/structure/designing-packages.md
msgid "Use package-prefixed parameter keys, route names, event handler IDs, and DI aliases."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/structure/designing-packages.md
msgid "Keep default configuration small and documented."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/structure/designing-packages.md
msgid "Avoid doing irreversible work during service registration."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/structure/designing-packages.md
msgid "Put optional integrations in separate config files or providers when they require optional Composer packages."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/structure/designing-packages.md
msgid "Test the package inside a minimal Yii application so the config plugin, DI container, routes, console commands, migrations, translations, and assets are exercised together."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
